          "reviewBody": "Nice School.Good Amenities and has every sports facilities except Table Tennis and Lawn Tennis. But work on both the coaches is still going so after some time you would get to see a table tennis coach as well as a lawn tennis coach. The principal is a very fine gentleman and also motivates everybody during his speeches every Monday. The teachers are also very polite. I have studied here for almost 9 years till now (it's 2020).Boarding facility is also available.\nAchintya Pasricha",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
